data.description: NO MORTGAGE PAYMENT UNTIL MAY 2024 AND CLOSING COSTS PAID BY SELLER!!! Along the storied streets of the coveted Trimmier Estates you will find this timeless gem ready to be made into a home. Upon entry you will appreciate the convenience of the French door adorned office off to the right allowing for a perfect separate setting for a FOURTH bedroom, homework or for a work-from-home setup. Continuing on, the freshly installed gray Luxury plank floors coupled with a custom 8-foot barn door catapult you into a modern open floorplan perfect for entertaining, gatherings, or a cozy night by the fireplace! Also, downstairs you will find a bright kitchen complete with custom backsplash, a complementing kitchen island, and a conveniently located half bathroom. Behind that glorious barn door and heading upstairs you will walk directly into an expansive loft, perfect for a second living room or family theater space. To your left you will enter a Texas-sized premiere suite, complete with a bathroom large enough for a sitting area! Also, upstairs you will find two more sizable bedrooms, one already customized for a princess, and a dedicated bathroom! This home is located a mere 12 minutes from Fort Cavazos, and a short 45 minute drive from the largest indoor waterpark in the country, Kalahari! Book your tour today, 411 E. Little dipper awaits your presence.
